Class PartTimeEmployee

  • java.lang.Object
    • EmployeeInfo
      • PartTimeEmployee
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class PartTimeEmployee
extends EmployeeInfo
    A subclass of EmployeeInfo for part time employees. Stores the employee's hourly wage, hours worked per week, and weeks worked per year.
    See Also:

        Parameters:
        employeeNumber - the employee number.
        firstName - the first name.
        lastName - the last name.
        sex - the sex (0 is male, 1 is female, 2 is other).
        workLocation - the work location.
        deductionsRate - the deductions rate (between 0.0 and 1.0).
        hourlyWage - the hourly wage.
        hoursPerWeek - the number of hours worked per week.
        weeksPerYear - the number of weeks worked per year.
